Description: Fragment of papyrus, with remains of 15 lines of a Coptic text written along the fibres (recto) probably from same manuscript as 75424. 75421-75426 are mounted together.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380668) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380668)
